'''Cody Gibson''' (born September 11, 1987) is an [[United States|American]] [[mixed martial arts|mixed martial artist]] who competes as a [[Bantamweight (MMA)|bantamweight]] in the [[Ultimate Fighting Championship]].

At [[UFC 170]] Gibson lost to [[Aljamain Sterling]] by decision.<ref>http://mmajunkie.com/2014/02/ufc-170-results-photos-aljamain-sterling-hangs-on-to-beat-cody-gibson</ref>

At [[UFC Fight Night: Swanson vs. Stephens]] Gibson defeated [[Johnny Bedford]] by TKO.<ref>http://www.visaliatimesdelta.com/story/sports/2014/06/29/visalias-cody-gibson-earns-first-ufc-win-seconds/11706243/</ref>

At [[UFC 178]] Gibson lost to [[Manvel Gamburyan]] by submission.<ref>https://sports.yahoo.com/news/ufc-178-prelims-results-recap-015826579.html</ref>

